{"tid":2376831,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前希古恩女伴：他愛淫蕩的女人","createTime":"2021-01-23T05:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T06:24:20.000Z","uid":234948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64db7515cdbcc437d73cde275665ce6b7dba5878","tid":2376831,"uid":234948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】國際邁阿密射手希古恩被前女伴爆料，原來他最愛淫蕩的女人。<br />\n<br />\n身材勁吸睛的Manuela Ferrera最近現身意大利足球節目《Tiki Taka》，自爆與曾於意甲征戰多年的希古恩（Gonzalo Higuain）搭上。「我們從未正式拍拖，但有數個月都常常相聚。不過，由於他有女友，所以我們分開了。他對於淫蕩的女人特別有興趣。」Manuela說。希古恩在意甲征戰多年，當中以效力拿玻里最長時間，但Manuela透露跟希古恩在一起時，他正效力AC米蘭，即2018年8月至2019年1月。Manuela也曾跟現效維多利亞的葡萄牙名將哥利斯馬在一起。她透露這位翼鋒很喜歡煮飯：「我們拍拖8個月，他很喜歡我煮的西蘭花意粉。」"},{"pid":"aafbfde7a754e951e05e85c5c9a0255dd78c9e34","tid":2376831,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"dda8116677b55e77730d404d69ba1d741c113358","tid":2376831,"uid":42246,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"有邊個男人唔鐘意淫蕩sp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdfc9030f7f2493e8c2d7cc17d852d3d6af7567","tid":2376831,"uid":101307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:59:11.000Z","msg":"唔通愛死魚咩 大波冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3618a64ade59b84f95d0233372ffcf7a43f44f85","tid":2376831,"uid":298114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dda8116677b55e77730d404d69ba1d741c113358","tid":2376831,"uid":42246,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"有邊個男人唔鐘意淫蕩sp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀老婆就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4317c6850b59ac0e814f31f2dec72df748e505","tid":2376831,"u